{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_53_03",
  "title": "川咲さくら 3話 私の心もピカピカ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――四月三日　夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ～、美味しかったぁ～\nごちそうさまでした！　ケーキありがとね、愛ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、喜んでもらえて何よりです！\nよし、それじゃあ後片付けしちゃいますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5566.666666699998,
          "startTime": 20.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6899.999999999998,
          "startTime": 22.2333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clean-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8533.333333399998,
          "startTime": 23.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clean-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8533.333333399998,
          "startTime": 23.8666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clean-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8533.333333399998,
          "startTime": 23.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、私がやるよ！　えっと、食器を下げて\nそれからテーブルを拭いて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ、ゆっくりしてて下さい！\nさくらさんのお誕生日なんですから\n片付けも私がやります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、こういう時こそやりたいの\n誕生日だからこそ気を引き締めたいというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、みんなで暮らしている寮だから\nどんな時でも感謝の気持ちは忘れないようにしたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5666694641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "という訳だから、私にも片付けのお手伝いをさせて\nほしいな。せっかくだし、寮の掃除もしちゃおっか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらさん……！　そういうことなら分かりました。\n私も一緒にやらせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "よし、大体綺麗になったかな？\n……あっ、冷蔵庫の下、ほこりが溜まってるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5333340962,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4900.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 76.4333340962
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "狭いので、手だと届かなさそうですね\nそこは日を改めて掃除する方がいいのでは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "でも気付いちゃったし……。あの棒使えば取れそう！\n日頃の感謝を込めて、今やっちゃおう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。そうですね！\n日頃の感謝を込めて綺麗にしちゃいましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4666674296,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9466.666666600006,
          "startTime": 104.9333340962
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10100.00000000001,
          "startTime": 105.5666674296
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10713.3333333,
          "startTime": 106.1800007629
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11313.333333300008,
          "startTime": 106.7800007629
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ライトの上の所、汚れが……\n椅子、椅子っと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　シンクがちょっと曇ってるかも？\nせっかくだし磨こうかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5333203633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ～……気付けばこんな時間まで……\n目につくとやりたくなっちゃうというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ちょっとで済ませるつもりだったのに……\nいつの間にか、私のお誕生日、終わっちゃってたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふっ……あはははっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1999965669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "頑張り過ぎちゃいましたね。でも、寮だけじゃなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.0666713716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんだか、私の心もピカピカになった気がします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2000083923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん、私もだよ！　おかげで素敵な誕生日の",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.0999986013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "締めくくりになったよ。ありがとね、愛ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2333417256,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}